      • VERSION_NUMBER

        public static final java.lang.String VERSION_NUMBER
        The current script version number - should be convertible to a double precision number for comparison reasons. Note - script version should always be less then CNUViewer version number and script version should only increase when new commands are added not just when CNUViewer is updated
